title: Starts of the Week + Week 15 Breakdown, Farewell to Urban Meyer - Fantasy Football Podcast for 12/16
description:
Week 15 is underway and The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason dive into Week 15 matchups and reveal their Starts of the Week! Plus, injury updates, a new edition of “Never Not Working,” and the Boom Boom Kicker story continues! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast! -- Fantasy Football Podcast for December 16th, 2021.
 (4:45) - Never Not Working
 (12:10) - NFL News
 (28:10) - Fantasy Forecast 
 (28:25) - Raiders at Browns
 (33:00) - Patriots at Colts
 (36:25) - Panthers at Bills
 (40:25) - Cardinals at Lions
 (47:00) - Jets at Dolphins
 (52:55) - Cowboys at Giants
 (56:45) - Football Team at Eagles
 (01:00:25) - Starts of the Week
 (01:01:10) - QB Starts of the Week 
 (01:04:00) - RB Starts of the Week 
 (01:06:35) - WR Starts of the Week
 (01:08:15) - TE Starts of the Week
 (01:10:20) - Boom Boom Kicker of the Week
